text: Mahmoud Abdel Aziz (born 27 July 1990) is an Egyptian professional footballer who plays as a midfielder for Zamalek SC. In May 2018, he was named in Egypt’s preliminary squad for the 2018 FIFA World Cup in Russia. ==Honours== Zamalek SC * Egypt Cup: 2018, 2019 *Egyptian Super Cup: 2019–20 * Saudi-Egyptian Super Cup: 2018 * CAF Confederation Cup : 2018–19 * CAF Super Cup: 2020 ==References== ==External links== * Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:Egyptian footballers Category:Egyptian Premier League players Category:Zamalek SC players Category:Association football midfielders Category:Egypt international footballers
title: Mahmoud Abdel Aziz (footballer)
